MOTIVATED! Great potential*3 acres (app)+  2835SF* Seller  offering First Class Upgrade Home Warranty* new roof* $5000 carpet allowance with acceptable offer* .. Secluded with Privacy and nestled among woods and trees this home is located in the Brandon School District and ready for your special touches* Beautiful Le Bourgeois Estates .. This traditional 2-story home features  4 bedrooms + 3 1/2 baths and a large Bonus Rm for office/ exercise / 5th Bdrm*
The Family Rm offers a fireplace*Kitchen + Breakfast Rm*Master bedroom is on the main floor w/2 large walk-in closets* Spacious bedrooms* 
Outside ''Bonus'' features an above ground pool ('as is') nestled with a surrounding deck! Refrigerator, washer and dryer remain ''as is, at no value.''  Wonderful neighborhood of gorgeous acreage in Brandon school district!! Great potential!
